overview: Best Friends, Chuck and Trent?, are poppin' dogs and talkin' hogs with "EC3" Ethan Carter. That's right, everybody's favorite hog talkers are back in the saddle again. This time EC3 ponies up, grabs a cream boy and has the dongiest of times. This is the penultimate episode of dick and ball jokes. Not to be missed! Second only to Teddy Hart in tallywhackin' talk.
title: Best Friends With "EC3" Ethan Carter
